HEADWORD: Accend
<hw>Ac*cend"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>accendere</ets>, <ets>accensum</ets>, to kindle; <ets>ad</ets> +
